Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:06.52,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Agnese?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.17,0:00:12.01,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:16.17,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here on the Queen of the Adriatic Sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.96,0:00:18.07,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.34,0:00:21.44,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,There was some trouble and we ended up boarding this ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:27.30,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,So, the Queen of the Adriatic Sea is the name of this ice fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:30.06,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,The name of this fleet is "The Queen's Fleet".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:32.29,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,This ship is just one of many frigates.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.29,0:00:34.82,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you really don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:37.95,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:41.35,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,I'm helping search for intruders.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:43.01,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.01,0:00:45.75,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're the intruders...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.50,0:00:48.25,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,I can make use of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.71,0:00:50.53,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,We were dragged into this unaware.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:53.94,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep talking like that, then I'm going to scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:58.02,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,I advise you not to anger me if you want to escape this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.36,0:01:03.26,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we'll have to listen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:08.07,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,How do you benefit from helping us escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.87,0:01:13.56,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,A reward... you can think of it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:50.96,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What is this "Queen's Fleet" anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:55.96,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fleet crafted to observe the Adriatic Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:03:00.06,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:04.84,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,We've only gathered fragments of the complete story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:08.24,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,We were suddenly attacked by the people on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:12.95,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Is this fleet really only for observation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:16.66,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you were literally caught by that observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:21.23,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,You're the people who ruined the Roman Catholics' plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.23,0:03:25.92,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,One of you all the way from Japan, the other from London.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:28.74,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,To be fair, that's a superficial excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:30.48,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,This is a labor facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:36.75,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,Where sinners like me are gathered to pay for our failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:42.97,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,So the people on this ship are mostly from my squad, or rather from my ex-squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:45.24,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move on to the main topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:52.62,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for letting you go, I want you to rescue Sister Lucia and Sister Angelene.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:55.82,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,By rescue you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:04:01.11,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,Those two used a spell which dismantled the security, allowing for their escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:07.03,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,They were planning on rescuing the rest of us after preparing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:14.43,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:17.43,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,they were recaptured and are being lectured?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:21.04,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,They have to seal the hole that allowed those two to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:25.74,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to make modifications so that they can't use that spell again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:26.20,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Modify?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:30.72,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,So they're going to remove their ability to think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:33.62,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it will smash their brain structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:37.57,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to save them before that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:39.81,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,That is my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:42.07,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,We'll acquire the escape spell as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:47.20,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,But don't the Roman Catholics know of this spell already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:50.35,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen's Fleet has a huge job to do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:52.95,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,They shouldn't worry about one or two escapees.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:57.92,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go to the flagship to to distract them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:04:59.94,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,Please act during that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:01.94,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:04.88,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not helping you, I'm using you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:06.59,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you a prisoner as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:07.38,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Let's escape together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:11.99,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,The supervisors fear mutiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:17.15,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a psychological safety mechanism that's meant to prevent this from happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:20.98,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,I can freely move about the fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:23.04,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,I'm excused from labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:25.31,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,This place is comfortable for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:29.58,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,The efforts of Sister Lucia and Sister Angelene are going to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:33.85,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,They should've just escaped on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:39.68,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,And, if you can escape from here safely, don't ever get involved with the Roman Catholics again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:42.09,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:45.18,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But we're outnumbered, there's a chance we won't be able to save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:50.84,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,Is this an appropriate line for the man who challenged an army of Sisters?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.51,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:11.90,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,Those vestments were designed with a magically binding effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:20.09,Index II main,Index,0000,0000,0000,,If that was The Queen's Fleet,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:22.52,Index II main,Index,0000,0000,0000,,then I can't handle this by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:28.42,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,No one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:31.95,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Agnese said it's mostly unmanned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:37.40,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That must be where Lucia and Angelene are being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:39.38,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:41.34,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:44.75,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back, Orsola!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:58.20,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This armor is kind of like a magical robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:07:02.04,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it seems like part of the ship changed shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:11.08,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:16.61,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,How do you think we broke this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:20.89,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, I casually said it in Japanese, but you understand me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:23.62,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't listen to my warning,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.62,0:07:25.57,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be forced to use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:30.74,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:34.46,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we'll believe those words?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:35.23,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.11,0:07:41.62,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,According to Agnese, you can use a spell to get away from this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:44.89,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,She said we should cooperate with you to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:47.44,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Agnese said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:50.16,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,Consider the possibility that this is a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:52.41,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,This is enemy territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:58.73,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think we'd come all the way here, and using Agnese's name too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:02.52,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Lucia...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.50,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.81,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,Your words make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:12.31,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So, how do we escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.81,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,It's too troublesome to explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:16.44,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Angelene.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:18.23,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:25.93,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:28.76,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,By altering the spell that binds the ship into ice,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:30.29,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,we can open holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:35.79,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,With this, we can solidify seawater to form an underwater pathway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:38.31,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:43.44,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,T-They've added a counter spell to our binding clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:48.22,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,If we break the stitching in a certain pattern, the restraining spell will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.06,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:53.66,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, we can use my{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:59.21,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, so you mean to strip them naked too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:23.76,Index II main I,Angelene [childhood],0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:28.66,Index II main I,Agnese [childhood],0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, I'm concerned with what's for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:30.28,Index II main I,Lucia [childhood],0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:32.34,Index II main I,Agnese [childhood],0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more important than the Lord in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:35.08,Index II main I,Angelene [childhood],0000,0000,0000,,I'm concerned about that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:38.94,Index II main I,Angelene [childhood],0000,0000,0000,,We've had our food flavored with olives for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:41.33,Index II main I,Angelene [childhood],0000,0000,0000,,The bathwater is too hot, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.84,Index II main I,Lucia [childhood],0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about the flavoring!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:46.12,Index II main I,Lucia [childhood],0000,0000,0000,,And the bath is lukewarm, not hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:48.19,Index II main I,Angelene [childhood],0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:52.05,Index II main I,Angelene [childhood],0000,0000,0000,,It's true that the adults don't seem to mind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:54.31,Index II main I,Angelene [childhood],0000,0000,0000,,Are you{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:57.42,Index II main I,Lucia [childhood],0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:10:00.84,Index II main I,Angelene [childhood],0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to talk with them, then I'm coming along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:05.17,Index II main I,Agnese [childhood],0000,0000,0000,,That's right, that might be nice, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:11.41,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,When we will meet with Sister Agnese?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:13.57,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:16.74,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Agnese probably won't be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:20.54,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,She said that, in order to help us, she's going to create a distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:23.83,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that she went to the flagship of The Queen's Fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:25.29,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't joke around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:31.30,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen's Fleet was created to protect the ceremonial place for a large scale magical ritual, the Queen of the Adriatic Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:32.73,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen of the Adriatic Sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:36.22,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,We know that it will be activated on the flagship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:41.88,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,And the key to activation is another spell called the Appointed Time of the Rosary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:46.32,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,And that Sister Agnese is required for the Appointed Time of the Rosary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:50.04,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen to Agnese?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:57.34,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know the details, but at the very least her brain will be destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.79,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,leaving a body with only the heart beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:05.35,Index II main I,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen's Fleet has a huge job to do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:08.85,Index II main I,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,They shouldn't worry about one or two escapees.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:13.69,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,An attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:15.07,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,From where?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:19.51,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,No way, from the other ships...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.07,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,The Divine Cannon of St. Barbara?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:44.06,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth are you shooting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:47.04,Index II main,Biagio,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know, Sister Agnese?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.81,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,Bishop Biagio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:53.59,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ship 37 was sunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:57.01,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we continue to fire we'll hit the shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:12:02.86,Index II main,Biagio,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the dealings with others to my subordinates. It does not concern me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:08.94,Index II main,Biagio,0000,0000,0000,,If something were to happen to you, we would be unable to restore anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:10.53,Index II main,Agnese,0000,0000,0000,,It's really ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.53,0:12:12.35,Index II main,Biagio,0000,0000,0000,,The Appointed Time of the Rosary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:18.30,Index II main,Biagio,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have thought that only a heretic like you would be compatible with the spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:21.80,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bishop Biagio, we have an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:23.07,Index II main,Biagio,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:26.97,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,A giant vessel has been detected beneath where number 37 was sunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.76,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to be salvaging the remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:30.94,Index II main,Biagio,0000,0000,0000,,An underwater spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:40.87,Index II main I,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Orsola and others?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:43.72,Index II main I,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:50.14,Index II main I,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I might actually die this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.47,0:12:57.51,Index II main,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:00.63,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Index?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:03.05,Index II main,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:04.30,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:13.57,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Tatemiya Saiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:14.37,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:17.06,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,The substitute Supreme Pontiff of the Amakusa Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:21.22,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,But currently we're affiliated with the Church of England.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:22.95,Index II main,Itsuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Please use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:26.05,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:27.07,Index II main,Itsuwa,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:32.96,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:34.05,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Orsola and others?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:37.71,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,We picked up everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:41.24,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,We're currently interrogating the men elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:42.42,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:45.81,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the secret base of the Amakusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:50.16,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a building.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:52.37,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No way, is this{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:58.64,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to call it a submarine,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:00.72,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not such high-tech.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:04.25,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a wooden ship that can go underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:06.01,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,It's a ship that can float and sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:11.19,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You brought something like this to help with moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:14.22,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,It's expected that we'd bring our weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:18.72,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, we specialize in naval warfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:22.81,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,Paper is made from wood, and wood also makes ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:29.11,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Agnese...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:30.67,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:31.67,Index II main,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:35.52,Index II main,Index,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what we do next, we need details about what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:37.76,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should ask Lucia or Angelene{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:40.90,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:47.16,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you're alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:50.80,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to be so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:57.49,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,Those two outfits were restraining uniforms that the Roman Catholics prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:14:59.67,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,You're a slow guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:03.59,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,When you were unconscious, we used your right hand to destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:09.00,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.97,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:16.16,Index II main,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.71,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Getting angry because of this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:21.71,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So unreasonable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.66,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:25.65,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.21,Index II main overlap,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This is weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.21,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sister Agnese is still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:32.70,Index II main overlap,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Such a powerful bite attack! Why can't you defend yourself against other magicians?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:32.70,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,We still have work to do. We need to discuss what to do about Sister Agnese...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:36.78,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This poses an even greater threat than those 103,000 grimores!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:45.57,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuwa, this is your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:47.23,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss him on the earlobe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:49.14,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to explain the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:50.00,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.68,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:53.24,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, please listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:57.86,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:08.70,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sister Angelene...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:12.05,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,W-We were always doing things like this in our squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:14.66,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,So I carelessly did it out of habit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:17.60,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,Always?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:23.91,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,I like chocolate con panna more than coffee or tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:24.32,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:27.76,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,It's a hot chocolate drink with fresh cream on top{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:29.70,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Angelene!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:31.68,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,A Christian shouldn't be so attached to food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:32.39,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:33.18,Index II main,Itsuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:34.96,Index II main,Itsuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Please use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:37.86,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:39.40,Index II main,Itsuwa,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:44.54,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Again with the hot towel plan, Itsuwa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:45.79,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going far too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:49.98,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, to be unable to make progress is part of Itsuwa's charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:55.34,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the "Queen of the Adriatic Sea" the name of the spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:17:01.72,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, the Venetians and Roman Catholics were on bad terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:08.66,Index II main,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen of The Adriatic Sea was prepared by the Roman Catholic Church to annihilate Venice with a single blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:11.99,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So it's like a bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:14.35,Index II main,Index,0000,0000,0000,,It's not only physically destructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:18.16,Index II main,Index,0000,0000,0000,,It would completely erase all history and culture of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:19.33,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,All?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:22.65,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that Sister Agnese doesn't know any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:26.42,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,If she knew, there's no way she would just stand quietly by.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:33.63,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, we have to rescue Agnese Sanctis before that spell is activated, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.58,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,it's going to be extremely difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.66,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, we have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:43.20,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry, Sister Agnese will be crippled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:45.59,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,Do you expect us to sit by and do nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:53.56,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Agnese has always taken care of me, so I can't let it go without repaying her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:55.61,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,We're up against a powerful foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:59.33,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,If we set up the underwater pathway, we might be able to stop the fleet from moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:03.22,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that we can defeat the enemy just by halting their movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:06.18,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:09.92,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tatemiya. Isn't that enough already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:10.54,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:18.57,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What we should discussing isn't whether to save Agnese or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:24.08,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,She gave up her own freedom in order to allow her friends to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:29.08,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't act, her kind intentions will be destroyed after she's used.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:31.92,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So we have to go and save her, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:35.30,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,We'll also protect Venice from being destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:38.67,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then, there's only one thing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:41.34,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to save her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:43.45,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:49.95,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, that problem had already been settled right from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:52.50,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,I've already prepared a strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:56.61,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,I just needed to make sure you were ready for this or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:18:58.88,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Tatemiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:03.77,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! We're going into battle, but everyone must come back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:06.98,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,What has the Priestess taught us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:09.20,Index II main,[Crowd],0000,0000,0000,,To reach out to all those in need!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:16.76,Index II main,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:18.11,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:22.50,Index II main,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Since I can't use it, I thought it might be better if you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:27.10,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Index?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:28.08,Index II main,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:31.69,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:32.90,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.01,Index II main,Agata,0000,0000,0000,,Bishop Biagio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:41.23,Index II main,Agata,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy fleet inbound! About 30 to 40 ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:43.69,Index II main,Agata,0000,0000,0000,,50 seconds until they reach our position.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:45.39,Index II main,Biagio,0000,0000,0000,,Sink them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:46.27,Index II main,Agata,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:56.32,Index II main,Agata,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't shooting back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:57.49,Index II main,Agata,0000,0000,0000,,Can it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:19:59.07,Index II main,Agata,0000,0000,0000,,All hands, take defensive positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:02.37,Index II main,Biagio,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:02.93,Index II main,Agata,0000,0000,0000,,They're fireships!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:05.80,Index II main,Agata,0000,0000,0000,,A fleet of unmanned boats filled with explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:12.90,Index II main,Agata,0000,0000,0000,,A large vessel is approaching from a depth of 40 meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:14.35,Index II main,Agata,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely a submarine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:20.06,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike on the enemy sub confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.06,0:20:21.58,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy forces have boarded ship 29!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:23.80,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Amakusa from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:25.80,Index II main,Agata,0000,0000,0000,,No way, the sub was a decoy too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:28.02,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about taking control of every ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:31.35,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,We need only think about destroying the enemy core.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:34.48,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,You guys head to the Queen of the Adriatic Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.04,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:39.53,Index II main,Tatemiya,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:41.52,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:20:58.61,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:20:59.26,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:01.73,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,These idiots...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:04.76,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you move to save Sister Agnese?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:11.89,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,They're firing at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:13.86,Index II main,Orsola,0000,0000,0000,,They're hoping to sink us along with the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:16.24,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're targeting us directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.24,0:21:17.31,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:19.26,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, one of the twelve disciples,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:23.53,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,tax collector and lowly servant of the eradicating magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:31.12,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:38.76,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, one of the twelve disciples{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:42.05,Index II main,Angelene,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:48.82,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Angelene!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.73,0:21:51.81,Index II main,Lucia,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Angelene!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:29.45,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,We boarded the flagship to prevent the Queen of the Adriatic Sea from activating.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.19,0:23:33.34,Index II main,Kamijou Touma,0000,0000,0000,,As one question after another remains unanswered, Index is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:35.88,Index II main,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: "Appointed Time of the Rosary"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.88,0:23:38.96,Index II main,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,At the time when science and magic cross, the story begins.
